# Local development secrets (copy to .dev.vars)
# See: https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/configuration/secrets/
#
# No secrets required for local dev -- API keys are stored in D1.
# Add any external service keys here as needed.
#
# Non-secret vars are set in wrangler.toml [vars]:
#   ENVIRONMENT  — "development" | "staging" | "production"
#
# D1 database binding (DB) is configured in wrangler.toml [[d1_databases]].
# Run migrations: pnpm db:migrate:local
# Seed an API key: pnpm seed
